data.description: Welcome to 2+ stunning acres in the heart of beautiful, established Carmichael. Nestled amongst the trees, this tranquil estate offers the potential for 3 homes! The main home features 4 bedrooms, beautiful wood beam ceilings in the family room, downstairs master suite, and a stunning updated kitchen. The second attached unit offers kitchenette, full bath, two rooms and its own private entrance. The third piece offers a 4 car garage conversion into a stunning game room with dance floor. Seize the opportunity for a business from your home in this two story building with half bath or make it complete for that third home. A great Air BnB potential. A stunning orchard offers endless fruit, the 1800+ Quonset hut is ready to store all of your tools, and the property is fenced and crossed fenced for all of your critters to enjoy. This rare Carmichael Charmer Estate will empress you with the endless possibilities and plenty of room for a hobby business, quilting, pottery, art, or design! Come enjoy the serene living and beautiful front porch views! Relax in the your private pool, spa and infrared sauna. Made for entertaining, this estate has it all!Plus, assumable VA loan!
